To Reset Your Password
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Click the following link:
It will take you to a webpage where you can enter your NEW password:
<%= link_to "Reset My Password", password_reset_url(@user.token) %>


If you do not click this link and change your password within 2 hours of submitting a password reset, the link will be invalidated for your security.
If this happens to you, simply visit the following page to apply again and we will send you a new link via email:
<%= link_to "Apply For Password Reset", forgot_password_path %>



